	onnect at Bombo Italian on Tuesday\, March 31 at 4:30 PM. Power Connect is
	 our signature networking series-an easygoing space to meet fellow LGBTQ\\
	+ and allied professionals\, reconnect with familiar faces\, and build rel
	ationships that support your business and our community. Come as you are\,
	 bring a colleague\, and expect the standard Power Connect vibes: warm wel
	comes\, real conversation\, and connections that keep going after the even
	t. What to Expect A welcoming\, relationship-first environment Space for c
	asual conversation and meaningful introductions A great chance to meet GSB
	A members\, partners\, and friends An easy way to plug into the GSBA commu
	nity Accessibility If you have access needs or accommodation requests\, pl
	ease reach out to GSBA in advance and we'll do our best to support you: me
	mbership@thegsb.org Thank You to Our Presenting Sponsor    Power Connect: 
	Bombo is presented by U.S. Bank\, supporting LGBTQ\\+ and allied businesse
	s and helping strengthen connections across our region.\n\nhttps://seatoda
	y.6amcity.com/events/#/details/power-connect-bombo/18234879/2026-03-31T00\
